FBIS4-57775 "drlat101_a_94003" FBIS-LAT-94-101 Daily Report 24 May 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba Jose Cabanas Appointed To Head Directorate Jose Cabanas Appointed To Head Directorate FL2505012094 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 2300 GMT 24 May 94 FL2505012094 Havana Radio Rebelde Network Spanish BFN [Excerpt] Miguel Alfonso, official Foreign Ministry spokesman, today reported that Jose Cabanas has been named to head the new Directorate for Affairs of Cubans Residing Abroad. This directorate was created as part of the agreement reached at the recent conference, The Nation and the Emigre Community. [passage omitted]
